@startuml 哪吒网络安全-API流式对话
' =============================================================================
' 哪吒网络安全 TUI —— DeepSeek API 流式对话序列图
' 描述: 从用户按 Enter 到完整响应渲染的 SSE 流式对话全流程
' =============================================================================

title 哪吒网络安全 —— DeepSeek API 流式对话序列图

skinparam backgroundColor #121218
skinparam defaultFontColor #DCDCE6
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #00D4FF
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #1E1E2E
skinparam participantBorderColor #32324B
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #1A1A2E
skinparam noteBorderColor #00D4FF
skinparam lifeLineColor #32324B

actor "用户" as User
participant "UI 输入区\n(process_key)" as Input
participant "App 状态\n(update())" as App
participant "DeepSeekClient\n(stream_chat)" as Client
participant "Tokio 后台任务\n(tokio::spawn)" as TokioTask
participant "DeepSeek API\n(api.deepseek.com)" as API

== 1. 用户输入与预处理 ==

User -> Input : 键入消息 "请分析这个漏洞"
Input -> Input : Enter 键触发
Input -> App : Action::SubmitMessage("请分析这个漏洞")

App -> App : 创建 User Message\n(Uuid, Role::User, content)
App -> App : 追加到 tab.messages
App -> App : 清空 input_buffer

== 2. 构建 API 请求 ==

App -> App : 将 tab.messages 转为 Vec<ApiMessage>
App -> App : 从 AgentConfig 获取 tools 定义

App -> Client : stream_chat(tx, tab_id, messages, tools)

note right of Client
  请求体 ChatCompletionRequest:
  - model: "deepseek-chat"
  - messages: [...]
  - tools: [...]
  - stream: true
  - max_tokens: 4096
end note

== 3. 发起流式请求 (后台任务) ==

Client -> TokioTask : tokio::spawn(async { ... })
activate TokioTask

TokioTask -> API : POST /v1/chat/completions\n(HTTPS + SSE)
activate API

TokioTask -> App : tx.send(StreamStart { tab_id, message_id })
App -> App : 创建空 Assistant Message\n追加到 tab.messages

== 4. SSE 流逐行解析 ==

group SSE 流式数据传输
    loop 每个 SSE chunk
        API --> TokioTask : data: {"id":"...","choices":[{"delta":{"content":"这个"}}]}

        TokioTask -> TokioTask : 逐行解析\n跳过空行\n跳过 "data: [DONE]"\n剥离 "data: " 前缀\nJSON 反序列化

        TokioTask -> TokioTask : process_stream_choice()

        alt delta.content 有值
            TokioTask -> App : tx.send(StreamChunk { tab_id, message_id, chunk: "这个" })
            App -> App : 查找 message_id\n追加 chunk 到 content
        else delta.tool_calls 有值
            TokioTask -> TokioTask : apply_tool_call_delta()\n累积 id/name/arguments
        end

        App -> App : 触发重绘
    end
end

API --> TokioTask : data: [DONE]

== 5. 流完成处理 ==

TokioTask -> API : 连接关闭
deactivate API

TokioTask -> TokioTask : 提取 usage (prompt_tokens, completion_tokens)

TokioTask -> App : tx.send(StreamDone {\n  tab_id, message_id,\n  content, usage\n})

App -> App : 累加 Token 用量\n(tab.total_usage)
App -> App : 计算费用\n(usage.cost(&pricing))
App -> App : 更新 status_message\n("完成 - Token: 150P + 380C | 费用: ¥0.0034")

deactivate TokioTask

== 6. 最终渲染 ==

App -> App : 触发重绘
Input -> User : 屏幕显示完整 AI 回复

note over User, API
  <b>全流程耗时分解:</b>
  - 请求构建: < 1ms
  - 网络延迟 (TCP+TLS): ~50-200ms
  - 首个 Token (TTFT): ~200-800ms
  - 流式传输: 取决于 Token 数量
  
  <b>错误处理路径:</b>
  - HTTP 状态码 ≠ 200: StreamError
  - 流读取异常: StreamError
  - JSON 解析失败: 跳过该行，继续
end note

center footer 哪吒网络安全 TUI · SSE 流式对话 · 完整生命周期
@enduml
